column6: BRIEF TORNADO OBSERVED BY BOTH A SHERIFFS DEPUTY AND A SKYWARN SPOTTER NEAR JEFFERSON RIVER RD AND BROCKTON RD. DAMAGE TO TREES AND LIMBS. (FFC)

column8: NUMEROUS TREES DOWNED ACROSS THE COUNTY AND ROOF BLOWN OFF A HOME AT TIMBLE ROAD AND HEWELL ROAD. DAMAGE SURVEY SHOWED TORNADO PATH 3/4 MILE LONG AND 100 YDS WIDE. THRE (FFC)
